<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>682</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>zhí děng dào zhǔ lái 迦南682</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhí děng dào zhǔ lái, zhí děng dào zhǔ lái. yī qiè de ào mì dōu yào jiē kāi.
 zhí děng dào zhǔ lái, zhí děng dào zhǔ lái. yī qiè dōu huì míng míng bái bái.
 wèi shén me bù qíng yuàn chī kuī ne? wèi shén me bù qíng yuàn shòu qī ne?
 qǐ bù zhī bù yì de rén bù néng chéng shòu shén de guó, zhǔ kuài huí lái.</lyrics>
</song>